HEADWORD: pro-lifer
<hw>pro-lif"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who is opposed
to voluntary abortion; one who is pro-life, especially an activist in
the campaign to make abortion illegal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

